response.original_title: GCW vs Renegades of Wrestling Australian Tour 2023, August 27th
response.overview: It's August 27th and it's the final day of GCW's Australian Tour 2023 and their final stop is Eatons Hill Hotel in Australia. The first matches where the pro wrestling stars of GCW will collide with the pro wrestling stars of Renegades of Wrestling are already announced, check them below:  Joey Janela vs Outback Adam Gringo Loco vs Tim Hayden  Three Way Match Effy vs Bobby Bishop vs Cockroach  Maki Itoh vs Allie Katch El Hijo del Vikingo vs Mitch Ryder  Also in the lineup:  Tag Team Match PunchDrunk Istria & Steph De Lander vs. Charli Evans & Everett Connors  ROW Title Match Caveman Ugg (c) vs. Solomun Blackwell
response.title: GCW vs Renegades of Wrestling Australian Tour 2023, August 27th
